DescriptionThis is a table storing Cruise Ancillary Assocation Criteria.
Column NameData TypeNullableComments
ANC_ASSOC_CRIT_IDBIGINTYESThis is the Primary Key sequence for maintaining the Cruise Ancillary association criteria table. .
ANC_ASSOC_IDBIGINTYESThis is the foreign key referenced by cruise ancillary association table: ITRVL_CRU_ANC_ASSOC. .

DEP_ENDTIMESTAMP WITHOUT TIME ZONEYESThis field is used to store Departure end date .

PRIOR_POSTCHARACTER VARYING(20)YESThis field is used to store Prior or post. This will have value only in case of associated by is Day. .
OFFSET_BASISCHARACTER VARYING(20)YESThis field is used to store Offset basis. Possible values are Departure Date/Arrival date. This will have value only in case of associated by is Day. .
APPLY_ALSOCHARACTER VARYING(20)YESThis field is used to store Apply also. Possible values are CRUOVERLAP-Overlapping Cruises; CRUSAMEDEP-Cruises with same departure; CRUSAMEARR- Cruises with Same Arrival; NONE-None. This will have value only in case of associated by is Day. .
PORTCHARACTER VARYING(5)YESThis field is used to store Port. This will have value only in case of associated by is Port. .
APPLY_OVERLAP_CRUSMALLINTYESThis field is used to determine if to apply overlap cruise or not. Possible values are 0-No,1-Yes. This will have value only in case of associated by is Port. .
PORT_OCCRINTEGERYESThis field is used to store Port occurrence. This will have value only in case of associated by is Port. .
DAY_AT_PORTINTEGERYESThis field is used to store number of days at port. This will have value in case of associated by is Port. .
LAST_MODIFIED_BYCHARACTER VARYING(100)YESThis column stores the user who last modified the record. .
LAST_MODIFIED_DATETIMESTAMP WITHOUT TIME ZONEYESThis column stores the date for which the record was last modified. .
COMPANY_IDCHARACTER VARYING(20)YESThis field stores the Company ID. .

DEPPORT_CODETEXTYESThis field is used to store departure port code. .
ITINERARY_CODETEXTYESThis field is used to store itinerary code. .
SHIP_CODETEXTYESThis field is used to store ship code. .

This field is null for when the Cabin-Segment record is in free pool state (Not Covered, not booked, not allocated) .

CABIN_BKG_STATECHARACTER VARYING(20)YESThis column is used for tracking whether it is an actual Booking or a covered booking done in Real Inventory. This field will be populated for successful Real Inventory bookings against a Cabin. Possible values include - Booked - Booking is done completely (Specific Cabin/Auto assign cabin booking). Covered - Covered to booking scenario (For Unassigned Booking). null - Neither Booked nor Covered state. .
BOOKING_COVERAGEINTEGERYESThis column is used for tracking the Inventory Block ID against which the Cabin is booking-covered to a Block. A valid Block ID is set in this field only when a Cabin is booking-covered (via Unassigned booking) against a particular Block against a Cruise. .
SPACE_COVERAGEINTEGERYESThis column is used for tracking the Inventory Block ID against which the Cabin is space-covered to a Block. A valid Block ID is set in this field only when a Cabin is space-covered against a particular Block against a Cruise. Will be set in the event of Booking Coverage - provided if this chosen Cabin belongs to Free pool. Concerns the Real Inventory section - which involves Cabins. .
CAB_SEQ_NOCHARACTER VARYING(50)YESThis field stores the cruise cabin sequence number. .
IS_MKT_CATGSMALLINTYESThis column is a boolean flag saves true if record is a Marketing Category .
USER_IDCHARACTER VARYING(100)YESThis column is used to save the Logged In User ID in Domain Services while holding or unholding requested cabin. .
IS_WHEEL_CHAIRBOOLEANYESThis column is used to save whether the cabin supports wheel chair .
MKT_CATEGORY_CODECHARACTER VARYING(5)YESThis field stores marketing category code in case of marketing category booking or allocation to identify which cabin is covered for that marketing category. Ths field is saved only when real covered for mkt catg configuration is set as Yes. .
VERSIONBIGINTYESStores the last modified date in milliseconds. This is used for implementing locking mechanism to prevent concurrent updates .
PREFERRED_STATUSINTEGERYESThis field to set the cabin as either protected or prefered. 1 - prefered for cruise,2 - protected for cruise .
PREFERRED_CRUISE_CODECHARACTER VARYING(50)YESThis field is used to store the prefered/protected cruise codes .

MAX_CABIN_OCCINTEGERYESData point to store maximum cabin occupancy, It is a data coming from the cabin configuaration/ contract summary screen. This field can have values like 1,2,3,4,5 etc. .
IS_CONTRACTEDSMALLINTYESData point to understand whether the record is a cabin configuaration or contract summary. For a ship, the mode of operation can be owned/operated/third party. If owned there will not be any contract or supplier associated .So it will have cabin configuaraion. But in the case of operated or third party, it will have contrcat summary instead of cabin configuaration. Both these data we are keeping in this particular table and this field is to understand whether it is a contract record or configuaration summary record. .
